metadata.name: The Way You Look Tonight
metadata.description:
Mr. Owl met Miss Shiba on this lovely summer night
Up in the sky thousand stars, the moon was so bright
He wrapped her arms around her waste
He held her so tight
He said: “Oh Darling, I really love the way you look tonight.”
Miss Shiba blushed, said: “You fill my heart with light.”
They both felt in their heart, that this is so right.
To be continued…

LvB x MN
